reviews.review: No. Just no. Don't do it to yourself.

La primera media hora se basaba en puro chiste lo cual le quitaba mucha seriedad a la trama, pero luego fue tomando consistencia logrando asi un buen desarollo del villano, falto la informacion acerca de como fue la vida de Cap, Natasha y ademas tiene un final muy bien hecho

#InfinityWar es la primera película de Marvel Studios en la que le historia me hizo sentir que en realidad había algo en juego. Esa sensación de peligro inminente y de que los héroes se enfrentaban a un villano verdaderamente amenazante hizo de esta mi favorita en 10 años. 

No es la mejor obra y obviamente tiene algunos puntos débiles pero para mí, fue un gran parteaguas en este universo cinematográfico. #InfinityWar me deja muy contento, dandole un sólido 8.2/10
This is not a  movie about the avengers, it's a  movie about Thanos and that makes it incredibly good
After movie end.My brain still focus story next part.

I seen this movie the Thursday it came out but for some reason rotten tomatoes refused to let me voice my opinion. Infinity wars was a great movie we have waited all these years to see Thanos come and cause havoc and he did not disappoint the way he smashed Hulk at the beginning and then went on to put a beat down on the rest of the Avengers was great. You can tell that everyone from the actors to the people who made the coffee runs worked extra hard to make this movie a great  movie. The film looked amazing every thing was on point.The biggest shock tp me was when Redskull made a brief cameo appearance . The action was awesome and their was just enough comedy but it didn't bog down the movie. The only beef I had with the movie was no Hawkeye or Antman they needed to atleast have a small cameo. Look this movie was about Thanos and his road to capture the Infinity stones  and they did a very good job doing so. Everytime a Avengers movie comes out the bar gets raised high so part 4 has its work cut out and I can't wait to see it
Greatest movie of all time!!!! 100% recommended! The ending has you waiting for something magnificent in the future!
Awesomely depressing. Leaves you aching for more. Some minor issues I found with it but nothing major or hurtful.
If you’re a marvel fan & don’t like this, there’s something wrong with you.
I am at a loss for words.  I will not write a full review until I feel that I will not spoil anything.  This movie was brutal, funny, wondrous, and emotional.  Go see it before you get spoiled!
